# Media Queries ðŸ“

Apply CSS only if a certain condition is true.

```css
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  body {
    background-color: lightblue;
  }
}
```

- `max-width: 600px`: Styles apply if screen is 600px or smaller (Mobile).
- `min-width: 600px`: Styles apply if screen is 600px or wider (Desktop/Tablet).

# Common Breakpoints ðŸ“

Typical widths to target:

```css
/* Mobile devices */
@media (max-width: 480px) { ... }

/* Tablets/iPads */
@media (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 768px) { ... }

/* Laptops */
@media (min-width: 769px) and (max-width: 1024px) { ... }

/* Desktops */
@media (min-width: 1025px) { ... }
```
